     Unit Command/Head Last Name:  <%= @nomination.unit_commander_last_name %><br />
     Unit Command/Head Suffix:  <%= @nomination.unit_commander_suffix %><br />
     Unit Command/Head Phone:  <%= @nomination.unit_commander_phone %><br />
     Unit Command/Head Email:  <%= @nomination.unit_commander_email %><br />
     Unit Command/Head Organization:  <%= @nomination.unit_commander_organization %> <br/>
     </p>

     <p>
     NOMINATING OFFICIAL<br/>
     Nominating Official Rank/Title:  <%= @nomination.nominating_official_title %><br />
