     Nominating Official Last Name:  <%= @nomination.nominating_official_last_name %><br />
     Nominating Official Suffix:  <%= @nomination.nominating_official_suffix %><br />
     Phone Number:  <%= @nomination.nominating_official_phone %> <br/>
     Nominator Email:  <%= @nomination.nominating_official_email %> <br/>
    </p>

    <p>
    NOMINATING POINT OF CONTACT (POC)<br/>
